## Before submitting

- Grep new strings against docs/terminology.md §7 Deprecated and §10 quick reference.
- New adopted strategy → `config/strategy.yaml` + matching `strategies.yaml` entry (`layer: strategy`).
- New research topic → `config/research.yaml` only until graduated.
- Regime diagnostics → `config/regime.yaml` four axes (not a strategy).

Full glossary: `docs/terminology.md` · quick reference: §10 · audit checklist: `docs/terminology-audit.md`.
